Class PurchaseOrderProduct

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.beans.binding.ObjectExpression<T>
      • javafx.beans.binding.ObjectBinding<PurchaseOrderProduct>
        • RMA.PurchaseOrderProduct
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.beans.binding.Binding<PurchaseOrderProduct>, javafx.beans.Observable, javafx.beans.value.ObservableObjectValue<PurchaseOrderProduct>, javafx.beans.value.ObservableValue<PurchaseOrderProduct>
    public class PurchaseOrderProduct
extends javafx.beans.binding.ObjectBinding<PurchaseOrderProduct>
    PurchaseOrderProduct contains the specific information about a product coming from a purchase order in the RMA database.
